======  Known bugs  =======

The move/disappearing display of units is not complete.





========  Requires  ==========

Required opam packages (possibly non-exhaustive list)

ocamlbuild
ocamlfind

conf-gnomecanvas    (install the linux packages gtk, gtk-dev, gnome-dev, gnomecanvas-dev, cairo-dev)
conf-libev          (install libev-dev)

curses
fileutils
lablgtk
lwt_glib
lwt_react
lwt
pcre
react
text


